@{
    Layout = null;
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Facilities</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .facilities {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

            .facilities h1 {
                color: #004d99;
                font-size: 40px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                text-align: center;
            }

        .facility-card {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

            .facility-card:hover {
                transform: translateY(-10px);
                box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            }

            .facility-card img {
                width: 150px;
                height: 150px;
                border-radius: 8px;
                margin-right: 20px;
                object-fit: cover;
            }

            .facility-card h2 {
                color: #0056b3;
                font-size: 28px;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .facility-card p {
                line-height: 1.8;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="facilities">
            <h1>Our Facilities</h1>

            <div class="facility-card">
                <img src="/Content/Library.jpg" alt="University Library">
                <div>
                    <h2>Library</h2>
                    <p>Our library offers a vast collection of books, journals, and digital resources. It provides a quiet environment for study and research, equipped with modern amenities and comfortable seating.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="facility-card">
                <img src="/Content/Lab.jpg" alt="Laboratory">
                <div>
                    <h2>Laboratories</h2>
                    <p>We have state-of-the-art laboratories for various disciplines including science, engineering, and computer science. These labs are equipped with the latest technology to support hands-on learning and research.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="facility-card">
                <img src="/Content/SportsCenter.jpg" alt="Sports Center">
                <div>
                    <h2>Sports Center</h2>
                    <p>Our sports center includes facilities for indoor and outdoor sports such as basketball, tennis, and swimming. We promote a healthy lifestyle through various fitness and recreational activities.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="facility-card">
                <img src="/Content/StudentCafeteria.jpg" alt="Student Cafeteria">
                <div>
                    <h2>Student Cafeteria</h2>
                    <p>The cafeteria provides a variety of meal options, catering to different tastes and dietary needs. It’s a great place for students to relax, socialize, and enjoy a nutritious meal.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="facility-card">
                <img src="/Content/ConferenceHall.jpg" alt="Conference Hall">
                <div>
                    <h2>Conference Hall</h2>
                    <p>Our conference hall is equipped with modern audio-visual equipment and can accommodate large gatherings, seminars, and conferences. It’s a versatile space for academic and professional events.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>

